arts.ttl: Southend hit back to beat Rochdale in extra-time and reach National League semis
Eliminator Preview: Rochdale v Southend United
arts.sum: Only the three sides who finished above Dale during the regular season boast a better home record but the form book always seems to go out the window in the play-offs! Southend United on the other hand have only spent two match days of the entire season in the top seven - but you won't see Kevin Maher complaining.
